The problem was that `&lt;scope&gt;compile&lt;/scope&gt;` in my jackson dependency was missing.
It works like this:

        &lt;dependency&gt;
            &lt;groupId&gt;com.fasterxml.jackson.core&lt;/groupId&gt;
            &lt;artifactId&gt;jackson-annotations&lt;/artifactId&gt;
            &lt;version&gt;2.11.0&lt;/version&gt;
            &lt;scope&gt;compile&lt;/scope&gt;
        &lt;/dependency&gt;

I also had to add `classmate` with the same scope:

        &lt;dependency&gt;
            &lt;groupId&gt;com.fasterxml&lt;/groupId&gt;
            &lt;artifactId&gt;classmate&lt;/artifactId&gt;
            &lt;version&gt;1.5.1&lt;/version&gt;
            &lt;scope&gt;compile&lt;/scope&gt;
        &lt;/dependency&gt;

Finally, I had to add both entries to my **module-info.java** files:

    open module gui {
        ...
        requires com.fasterxml.classmate;
    }

and

    module core_entity {

        requires com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation;
        requires com.fasterxml.jackson.core;
        ...
    
    }

note the additional `com.fasterxml.jackson.core` requirement despite not having this explicit maven dependency.

