*Is there a way to use a variable in another method without using a parameter?*

Yes.  Here is one way:

```java
public class MyClass {

  private int myVar;

  public MyClass() {
    myVar = 0;
  }

  public void incrementMyVar() {
    myVar++;
  }
  
  public int getMyVar() {
    return myVar;
  }
}
```

